metadata.name: the roads we create
metadata.description:
this mural was created by ukrainian architect & contemporary artist asya gulak / autonomus digital art work and in the same time a part of the large-scale project 'padedo city' wich is which is being developed by ukrainian architects. 

resolution : 2500x2500px

*the owner of the mural will become the owner of a wall with the same mural in the city of padedo



**if you want to know more please contact asya directly
